Jetstar aircraft at Avalon Airport This article is about flights operated by Jetstar, and does not include Jetstar Asia or Jetstar Japan destinations. Jetstar flies to 19 domestic destinations and 15 international destinations in 9 countries across Asia, North America and Oceania. The company has been criticised by residents of the Australian Capital Territory for not serving Canberra Airport, which is Australia's eighth-busiest airport. Following is a list of destinations Jetstar flies to as part of its scheduled services as of April 2019.
